@startuml
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam style strictuml
skinparam defaultTextAlignment center
skinparam backgroundColor white

title FLI with Receiver-Supplied Stream Channels

participant "Sender" as S
participant "FLI\n(send handle)" as FSH
participant "Manager\nChannel" as MC
participant "Receiver's\nStream Channel" as RSC
participant "Receiver" as R

R -> MC: open_recv_handle(stream_channel=RSC)\n→ enqueue RSC descriptor
note left of MC: Sender dequeues RSC\ndescriptor from here

S -> FSH: open_send_handle()
FSH -> MC: dequeue RSC descriptor
MC --> FSH: RSC ready

S -> FSH: write(data)
FSH -> RSC: send message(s)
RSC --> R: data

S -> FSH: close → EOT
R -> RSC: close_recv_handle()

note over RSC
  RSC is NOT recycled to a
  main channel — it belongs
  to the receiver.
end note

@enduml
